    {
      "id": "39",
      "name": "推薦角色",
      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "customize",
          "data": {
            "data": {
              "parsed_content": [
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 1,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 27,
                      "icon_url": "https://bbs.hoyolab.com/hoyowiki/picture/character/Jean_icon.png",
                      "menu_id": 2,
                      "name": "琴",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:#ffffff"
                      ],
                      "text": "琴的定位非常多元，在打出可觀傷害的同時，又可以基於自身攻擊力為隊友提供大量的治療。因此，風鷹劍在提供高攻擊力白值的同時，被動效果也可以為琴帶來不錯的提升。",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 1,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 10,
                      "icon_url": "https://bbs.hoyolab.com/hoyowiki/picture/character/Keqing_icon.png",
                      "menu_id": 2,
                      "name": "刻晴",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:#ffffff"
                      ],
                      "text": "這是刻晴的另一個輸出流派。是在放棄元素反應後，僅憑超導與重擊作為主要輸出手段的物理流派。既然是",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:#ffe14b"
                      ],
                      "text": "物理傷害",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:#ffffff"
                      ],
                      "text": "，在單手劍中風鷹劍就是首選了！無論是被動效果還是副屬性皆可給刻晴帶來極大提升。",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            }
          }
        }
      ]
